arChildNodes.szComment: VANI turns, sees you, and freezes. The tavern goes quiet as the other villagers turn to gawk.
JOYFUL CLAPPING and a FIDDLER’S TUNE rise in the background (blends into next scene). VANI BOWS, humble.

CUT TO LATER: You drink from a MUG OF ALE, standing among dancing villagers as the tavern sways around you, warm and lively. 
You finish drinking and RAISE THE MUG toward your new friends. They pat you on the back, laughing.
Suddenly, you STAGGER.
You frown, touching your head... The room, music, and dancing figures start to BEND and CLOSE IN AROUND YOU. Warm smiles twist into menace. Something is very wrong. 
MOMENTS LATER: You DROP INTO A CHAIR at the table, limbs slack. Your vision darkens until--CRASH!
You SLUMP onto the table. MUSIC and DANCING STOP. Dead silence. The villagers lean in hungrily until Vani RAISES A HAND, stopping them.
A HIDDEN DOOR slides open. Vani and the villagers watch in silence as OSWEN emerges, PUSHES A CART to the table, and scoops your body onto it.
Oswen wheels you through the door and OUTSIDE into the snow. He pauses to turn a bitter look at you.

Oswen pulls the cart onward on a PATH THROUGH THE SNOW, freshly shoveled.
(OPENING CREDITS BEGIN.)
Slowly, OSWEN HUMS an EERIE MELODY.
En route to the BARN, you see a FEW VILLAGERS, busy with CHORES: One SPLITS LOGS. Two sit with their SNOW SHOVELS beside meager fires, staring hard-eyed as you pass.
Oswen arrives at the BARN DOORS and STOPS THE CART. He flexes his cold, sore hands as he moves to the doors and shoves one open, revealing a RITUAL CHAMBER.
Oswen WHEELS YOU INSIDE, past all manner of candle-lit horrors until finally stopping at a BLOOD-STAINED ALTAR.

Oswen moves to the altar and FINISHES HUMMING.
He pulls some blood petals from his pocket and starts to put them into the Hero’s mouth. 
He recites a prayer as he does so, but it’s difficult for him. 
The words are big and this is something he has heard Vani say that he is trying to remember.

He picks up a HOOKED BLADE. He tests the edge with his thumb.
You hear a DOOR OPEN (off camera)
Oswen speaks over his shoulder.

You hear the DOOR SHUT. Oswen returns to his work as the monk IOSEF, quick and quiet, CREEPS UP behind him, CLUB RAISED.
Oswen turns.
CRACK! IOSEF HITS OSWEN over the head, caving his skull.
OSWEN FALLS DEAD. Iosef scans the floor, frantic.

Iosef grabs a BUCKET OF UNKNOWN LIQUID and dashes it across your face.
You GASP and COUGH, suddenly able to move. There is SHOUTING OUTSIDE, growing louder.

YOU RISE from the cart, shake your head, and brandish your weapons. Iosef grabs his club as the BARN DOORS OPEN.
Vani speaks from O.S.
